<h4>4.3.1.3 Checkout and Order Verification</h4>
<p>During the routing pipe to Checkout, Context API data translates into precise database records. Customers can slide a numeric parameter to deduct Loyalty Points securely (algorithmically capped at 30% gross cart value). Selecting 'Cash on Delivery' automatically imposes a mandated 30% advance deposit barrier, enforcing immediate visual bank-slip upload components physically required for order progression.</p>

