<h4>4.3.2.1 Data Oversight and Inventory Engine</h4>
<p>Dashboards render React hook-fed KPI computations analyzing 24-hour traffic metrics. Inside Inventory grids, complex configuration arrays allow admins to continuously append nested rows (assigning Sizes matching distinct Flavors) directly propagating to Prisma relational fields establishing absolute product pricing matrices.</p>

