<h4>4.3.2.2 Comprehensive Order Management (Sub-Queues)</h4>
<p>Order processing is structurally partitioned to prevent pipeline bottlenecks:</p>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Standard Queue Panel:</strong> Rapid state mutation processing for catalog orders directly authorizing movement to Kitchen arrays.</li>
    <li><strong>Custom & Bulk Action Array:</strong> Specialized queues isolating complex evaluations targeting specific event dates and custom image structural feasibility checks prior to confirmation.</li>
    <li><strong>Payment Verification Desk:</strong> Strictly isolates orders flagged as <code>PENDING_VERIFICATION</code>. Admins cross-reference customer upload buffers representing Bank Slips against required 30% mathematical targets definitively clearing the order block.</li>
    <li><strong>Order History & Archiving:</strong> Searchable terminal maintaining <code>DELIVERED</code> profiles allowing historical Invoice generation instances dynamically mapped via PDF parsing routes.</li>
</ul>

