<h3>4.3.3 Role Interactions and Protocol Syncing</h3>
<p>Operational data syncs asynchronously blocking requirements for real-time contact routines.</p>

<div class="flow-box">
    <strong>Synchronous Payment Validation:</strong><br>
    Customer invokes the `PENDING_VERIFICATION` trigger via slip upload. Data immediately registers within the Admin Verification Queue. Administrator evaluates the image buffer successfully, mutating the boolean block clearing preparation constraints systematically.
</div>

<div class="flow-box">
    <strong>Background Urgency Polling:</strong><br>
    Configured Node-Cron daemons scan relational delivery parameter arrays exactly verifying 48-hour chronometric margins. Detecting proximity forcibly triggers SMTP Nodemailer warnings locking customer modifications while updating Admin queues displaying immediate 'Urgency' flags securely.
</div>

<h3>4.3.4 The End-to-End Order Pipeline Sequence</h3>
<ol>
    <li><strong>Selection Configuration:</strong> Customer mounts variant parameters via the Portal, accurately injecting additive metric equations.</li>
    <li><strong>Gateway Submission:</strong> Addresses form strings. Loyalty points execute validation algorithms checking 30% maximum caps. User initiates transaction protocols uploading verification image buffers.</li>
    <li><strong>System Acknowledgment:</strong> Record maps under the <code>NEW</code> constant. Admin queries parameters confirming structure, manually transitioning status mapping to <code>CONFIRMED</code>. System generates automatic email confirmation.</li>
    <li><strong>Preparation Guardrails:</strong> System denies native `PREPARING` progression lacking `Payment: True` dependencies. Admin executes visual cross-checks completing the `PENDING_VERIFICATION` array freeing the target to the Kitchen.</li>
    <li><strong>Delivery Notifications:</strong> Kitchen finalizes processing. Admin flags status <code>READY</code>. System sequentially initiates Node rules generating instant outbound Customer pickup alerts automatically.</li>
    <li><strong>Process Finality:</strong> Target delivery resolves. Admin marks <code>DELIVERED</code> processing outstanding physical COD balances into active Cashbook Income sectors mathematically. Database loop terminates accurately generating secure PDF invoice payloads definitively.</li>
</ol>

<h2>4.4 Quality Assurance Methodologies</h2>
<p>Continuous validation methodologies confirmed exact strict business computation parameters reliably.</p>
<p><strong>Frontend Regex Integration:</strong> Executed deliberate faulty keystrokes evaluating variable bounds successfully checking native error interceptors rejecting faulty arrays preventing backend corruptions effectively.</p>
<p><strong>Authentication Pen-Testing:</strong> Substituted expired JWT tokens testing external route fetches successfully resolving absolute native 403 authorization lockouts defending core database interactions inherently.</p>
<p><strong>System Workflow Stress Test:</strong> Replicated explicit lifecycle tracking loops originating from account mappings, variant generations, explicit cart additions integrating slip uploads dynamically verifying exact pipeline accuracy resulting in verified Cashbook balance resolutions maintaining absolute architectural consistency completely without fault instances.</p>

<h2>4.5 Technical Library Implementations</h2>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Prisma ORM:</strong> Prevents SQL injection utilizing compile-time safety checks standardizing parameters.</li>
    <li><strong>Bcryptjs:</strong> Implements Hash indexing protecting credentials globally from unauthorized retrieval attempts.</li>
    <li><strong>Nodemailer:</strong> Connects securely verifying SMTP protocols guaranteeing instant OTP verification array dispatches reliably.</li>
    <li><strong>Ant Design & Tailwind CSS:</strong> Radically accelerated exact visual output generations utilizing standard structural grids alongside utility classes reducing total stylesheet sizes.</li>
    <li><strong>Axios:</strong> Executed natively inside interceptors automating secure JWT attachments effortlessly across fetch sequences inherently.</li>
</ul>

<h2>4.6 Core Business Logic Implementations</h2>

<h3>4.6.1 Authentication & Isolation Rules</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Multi-Role Routing:</strong> Access strictly defined by <code>ADMIN</code> or <code>CUSTOMER</code> schema fields terminating unauthorized fetch loops securely.</li>
    <li><strong>Token Lifecycles:</strong> JSON Web Tokens specifically validate the Signature configurations executing verification logic securely across headers.</li>
    <li><strong>OTP Handshakes:</strong> Mandatory 6-digit confirmation logic specifically protects database blocks from automated SPAM registrations globally.</li>
</ul>

<h3>4.6.2 Dynamic Pricing Formulas</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Variant Algorithms:</strong> Mathematical formulation processing explicitly: <em>Final price = (Category Base Price * Size Multiplier) + Flavor Premium</em> dynamically accurately generating precise totals.</li>
    <li><strong>Bulk Deductions:</strong> Logic parsing triggers quantity variables. Hitting defined relational thresholds dynamically replaces base metrics executing hard "Bulk Price" discounts per unit specifically.</li>
    <li><strong>Boolean Guardrails:</strong> Logic filters <code>isAvailable</code> booleans stopping rendering explicitly nullifying any operations requesting functionally inactive sub-variant components inherently.</li>
</ul>

<h3>4.6.3 Strict Order Progression Pipeline</h3>
<table>
    <tr>
        <th>State</th>
        <th>Description</th>
        <th>System Validation Rules</th>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><strong>NEW</strong></td>
        <td>Order instantiation.</td>
        <td>Strictly processes Loyalty integer capping <= 30%. Calculates sub-48-hour delivery dates forcibly imposing priority numeric fees globally.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><strong>CONFIRMED</strong></td>
        <td>Admin review completed.</td>
        <td>Automatically invokes Nodemailer functions executing direct confirmation alerts securely.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><strong>PREPARING</strong></td>
        <td>Production phase logic.</td>
        <td><strong>Hard Block:</strong> Restricts status mutation. API explicitly rejects the change unless <code>Payment_Verified = True</code>.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><strong>READY</strong></td>
        <td>Production complete.</td>
        <td>Automatically triggers frontend dashboard notification variables targeting specific tracking UI components.</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
        <td><strong>DELIVERED</strong></td>
        <td>Process termination.</td>
        <td>Automatically resolves order fields generating backend PDF scripts pushing exact billing parameters asynchronously.</td>
    </tr>
</table>

<h3>4.6.4 Financial Ledger Algorithms</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Slip Validation Lock:</strong> Orders invoking COD variables naturally drop to <code>PENDING_VERIFICATION</code> triggering strict administrative observation loops required before operations advance securely.</li>
    <li><strong>Responsive Balances:</strong> Algorithm functions generating: <code>Total = Advance + Balance</code>. Altering specific items manually invokes recalculation rules maintaining explicit balance precision effortlessly.</li>
    <li><strong>Cashbook Integration:</strong> Administrators execute over-the-counter additions natively registering into daily chronological internal matrices processing net incomes accurately.</li>
</ul>

<h3>4.6.5 CRM Loyalty Mechanics</h3>
<ul>
    <li><strong>Ratio Increments:</strong> Native tracking logic applies 1 point strictly against each 100 Rs cart subtotal increment consistently.</li>
    <li><strong>Redemption Bounds:</strong> Validates user input deductions. Algorithm forces strict ceiling configurations negating attempts to formulate discounts effectively exceeding 30% gross cart variables unconditionally protecting base business margins inherently.</li>
    <li><strong>Penalty Extractions:</strong> Urgency algorithms trigger negative calculations extracting precisely 500 numeric integer points actively operating as systemic procedural priority surcharges.</li>
</ul>

